<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.3.1">
<l>kōvai vāyāḷ poruṭṭēṟṟi ṉerutta miṟuttāy matiḷilaṅkaik</l>
<l>kōvai vīyac cilaikuṉittāy kulanal yāṉai maruppocittāy</l>
<l>pūvai vīyā nīrtūvip pōtāl vaṇaṅkē ṉēluniṉ</l>
<l>pūvai vīyā mēṉikkup pūcuñ cānteṉ ṉeñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who broke the neck of bulls for the sake of her with a kōvai-red mouth, you who bent the bow</l>
<l>in order to destroy  the king of fortified Laṅkā, you who broke the tusk of the elephant good of family,</l>
<l>even though I don’t bow [to you] through [all] the time, strewing flowers [and] unending water,</l>
<l>my heart [is] the sandal paste that smears your body, which is a bilberry blossom.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
